1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,740
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,240
(Donghua Gate)
Guards.

4
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,439
(Donghua Gate)
Seize them all!

5
00:00:59,439 --> 00:00:59,840
Hurry!

6
00:01:00,159 --> 00:01:01,159
Quick!

7
00:01:01,159 --> 00:01:02,240
The people's hearts are a mirror.

8
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,479
They reflect the loyal and the corrupt.

9
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:05,200
Don't let yourselves be deceived.

10
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,439
Clear My Lord's name!

11
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,280
Kill them all.

12
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,120
Now!

13
00:01:11,359 --> 00:01:13,319
Release Lord Nine-Thousand!
He is innocent!

14
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,439
Release Lord Nine-Thousand!

15
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:17,400
Lord Nine-Thousand!

16
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:19,400
Lord Nine-Thousand is innocent!

17
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,319
Release him!

18
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:22,760
He is innocent!

19
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:25,159
My Lord.

20
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:26,359
Let us in!

21
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,040
Release Lord Nine-Thousand!

22
00:01:32,040 --> 00:01:33,400
Lord Nine-Thousand is innocent!

23
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,879
Lord Nine-Thousand is innocent!

24
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:35,840
My Lord.

25
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,120
He is innocent!

26
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,040
Lord Nine-Thousand!

27
00:01:41,879 --> 00:01:43,319
You useless fools!

28
00:01:43,640 --> 00:01:45,599
Can't even control your own daughters?

29
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:46,879
Mercy, Your Majesty!

30
00:01:46,879 --> 00:01:48,519
I have failed to teach
my daughter properly.

31
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,000
I won't

32
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,560
let my unfilial daughter go unpunished.

33
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,000
Mercy, Your Majesty!

34
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:53,079
Now you discipline them?

35
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:55,079
If anything happens to them,

36
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:57,239
won't that prove I am a tyrant?

37
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:00,799
Your Majesty.

38
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:03,239
Since noble ladies are among
the protesters,

39
00:02:03,239 --> 00:02:05,480
and their fathers are court officials,

40
00:02:06,079 --> 00:02:07,159
why not

41
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,520
execute them?

42
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:16,280
Then spread word

43
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:18,439
that the truth has been uncovered,

44
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:20,560
that these men deceived the throne,

45
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,240
and that His Majesty,
with his keen judgment,

46
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,879
has already dealt with them in private.

47
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:25,120
This way,

48
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,159
the people

49
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,479
can be temporarily appeased.

50
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,159
Your Majesty.

51
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,319
Mercy, Your Majesty!

52
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:35,759
Zhaohua, you truly know my heart.

53
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:36,960
Guards.

54
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:38,639
As Consort Rong has said,

55
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:40,759
take all of them away

56
00:02:40,759 --> 00:02:41,639
and execute them.

57
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,479
Mercy, Your Majesty!

58
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,039
Mercy!

59
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,680
Mercy, Your Majesty!

60
00:02:47,879 --> 00:02:49,000
Mercy!

61
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,520
Your Majesty.

62
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:53,879
Mercy, Your Majesty! Please!

63
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,919
Are you alright?

64
00:03:03,599 --> 00:03:04,199
I'm fine.

65
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,919
Feng Liu told me everything.

66
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,520
You single-handedly

67
00:03:12,199 --> 00:03:13,319
brought them all here

68
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:14,639
to testify for me.

69
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,520
Actually,

70
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,319
I didn't convince them to come back.

71
00:03:20,319 --> 00:03:22,319
When they heard you were in trouble,

72
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:23,919
they volunteered to return.

73
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,680
Besides,

74
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,680
you've helped me so much lately.

75
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,879
It's time I repaid you.

76
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:35,719
Then I'll have to work harder

77
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:37,000
to do more for you.

78
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,159
So you can keep repaying me.

79
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:48,879
My Lord.

80
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:49,400
My...

81
00:03:52,919 --> 00:03:53,919
Why is it that every time

82
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:55,199
I walk in on this?

83
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,159
Forget it.

84
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:58,199
I'll come back later.

85
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,000
Come back.

86
00:04:05,199 --> 00:04:05,800
What is it?

87
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,360
My Lord.

88
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,000
It's His Majesty.

89
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,360
Those officials,

90
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,360
His Majesty executed them all.

91
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,480
I'm not sure

92
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,519
if I'm overthinking this,

93
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:23,079
but I feel like Zhu Yunqi

94
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:26,160
has been under Rong Zhaohua's
control lately.

95
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,800
She's the one truly in power.

96
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,240
Now that I think about it,

97
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:31,360
you're right.

98
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:32,959
We can't let them

99
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,879
continue like this.

100
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,600
We need to find someone.

101
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,560
I received your carrier pigeon.

102
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,560
Everything has been arranged

103
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,439
as you instructed, My Lord.

104
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,480
Tomorrow,

105
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,920
I will lead my troops
to wait outside the city gate.

106
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:11,800
Are all other arrangements

107
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,240
in order?

108
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:13,839
Lord of Zhenbei.

109
00:05:14,959 --> 00:05:16,399
After the incident
with the noble ladies,

110
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,680
the people

111
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,439
are already filled with resentment
against Zhu Yunqi.

112
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,399
And Zhu Yunqi,

113
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:22,399
by slaughtering officials
in the palace recently,

114
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,959
has not only failed to quell the unrest,

115
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:27,199
but has made the other court officials

116
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,560
even more terrified of him.

117
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,800
So I believe now is

118
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,360
the best time for you

119
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,759
to show the people

120
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,199
that you are the true ruler.

121
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,279
I'll go prepare immediately.

122
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:40,800
Everything will be as you instructed.

123
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,199
He's the one you're looking for?

124
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,120
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

125
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:58,279
Lord of Zhenbei is ambitious

126
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,120
but timid by nature.

127
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:02,360
The rebellious ambition hidden
in his heart,

128
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,959
though it stirs restlessly,

129
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:05,199
has always been kept

130
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,639
firmly in the Emperor's grip.

131
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:09,879
I wasn't certain before

132
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:10,920
that he would actually show up.

133
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,680
But

134
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,879
can this alone

135
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,759
really overthrow the Emperor?

136
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,959
Of course not.

137
00:06:21,879 --> 00:06:22,959
I have other plans.

138
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,319
You did all this

139
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,839
for me.

140
00:06:36,120 --> 00:06:37,079
Was it worth it?

141
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:47,199
All these years,
I've worked with Zhu Yunqi,

142
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:48,600
me for revenge,

143
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,600
him for power,

144
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,120
each taking what we needed,

145
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,079
using each other.

146
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,560
Before this, I kept hoping

147
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:55,920
he could become a wise ruler,

148
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,600
govern the country well,

149
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,120
and let the people live in peace.

150
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,079
But I never expected

151
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:03,360
that everything now

152
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,600
is because I, in pursuit of revenge,

153
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,319
unleashed a beast.

154
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:12,660
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

155
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:17,079
So everything that's happened,

156
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,040
it all started with me.

157
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:22,079
And I should be the one to end it.

158
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,160
The agreed time has come.

159
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,759
Why isn't he making his move?

160
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,360
Lord of Zhenbei.

161
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,240
A message from My Lord.

162
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,240
The operation is canceled.

163
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,120
Canceled?

164
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:24,720
Feng Ye!

165
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:28,920
Why aren't you following the plan?

166
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,600
The plan has changed.

167
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:36,320
Let's discuss this further.

168
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,440
What changed?

169
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:41,080
Tell me!

170
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,600
You won't talk?

171
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,360
Then I'll see for myself.

172
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,879
It was for him.

173
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,200
Yukui.

174
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,039
Don't call me that.

175
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,759
My sister was right.

176
00:09:14,759 --> 00:09:16,720
All men

177
00:09:17,559 --> 00:09:19,240
are arrogant

178
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,759
and treat women as nothing.

179
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,639
Their words are all lies.

180
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,799
- But I
- I never meant to...

181
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:27,679
Trust me.

182
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:30,720
Give me a little more time.

183
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,200
Fine.

184
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,399
If you want me to trust you again,

185
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,240
then show me one more time.

186
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:48,639
Never mind.

187
00:09:49,879 --> 00:09:50,799
Yukui.

188
00:10:01,519 --> 00:10:02,679
Don't follow me.

189
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,000
Holy Maiden.

190
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:19,279
My Lord.

191
00:10:20,879 --> 00:10:21,799
Holy Maiden...

192
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:22,720
What happened to her?

193
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,759
Send someone to follow her.

194
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,399
Don't let anything happen to her.

195
00:10:26,759 --> 00:10:27,240
Yes.

196
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,780
(Ancestral Tablet of Late Father
Ruan Xiuyuan)

197
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:14,720
Father.

198
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:19,360
What should I do?

199
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:47,679
You're here.

200
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:51,679
It's been ages since my beloved zither,
Sting, last saw you.

201
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,960
It missed you.

202
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,240
Careful, Your Majesty.

203
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,519
Pluck that string too hard,
and you might get stung yourself.

204
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,600
The zither is fine,

205
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,879
but I'd rather not see it.

206
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:02,960
I heard

207
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:05,000
you brought Lord of Zhenbei here.

208
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:07,000
Why ask when you already know?

209
00:12:09,799 --> 00:12:11,840
You and I have known each other
since before we had anything.

210
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:13,600
Since childhood,

211
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,480
you devised the plans,

212
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,240
and I carried them out.

213
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,200
Amid oppression and persecution,

214
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,240
we stood together,

215
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,679
supporting each other,

216
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:25,080
and we fought our way to the throne.

217
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:28,039
I may be the supreme ruler,

218
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:29,399
but in my heart,

219
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,399
this realm

220
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,120
was always meant to be shared with you.

221
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,919
So I thought, some things,

222
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:39,039
you'd understand

223
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,919
even if I didn't say them.

224
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,919
But I never imagined

225
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,240
that one day,

226
00:12:46,679 --> 00:12:48,960
we would stand on opposite sides.

227
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,399
From the moment you began your tyranny

228
00:12:59,399 --> 00:13:01,960
and harmed innocent women,

229
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:04,360
all the bond between us

230
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,279
was buried by your own hands.

231
00:13:06,279 --> 00:13:07,159
Absurd!

232
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,279
One general's success
is built on ten thousand bones!

233
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:10,759
As the Emperor,

234
00:13:10,759 --> 00:13:12,480
one cannot afford to be soft-hearted.

235
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,519
Then your sword should be

236
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:17,159
pointed at the remnants of your enemies,

237
00:13:17,159 --> 00:13:18,960
never at your own people.

238
00:13:22,519 --> 00:13:25,320
Since when did Lord Nine-Thousand,

239
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,120
always ruthless and merciless,

240
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:28,519
learn to speak such high-sounding words?

241
00:13:28,879 --> 00:13:30,159
I think

242
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:32,759
it's clearly for that woman
of the Zhao Tribe.

243
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,120
If that's what you want to believe,

244
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,159
then so be it.

245
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,559
You summoned me here today.

246
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:42,240
Surely it's not just to say all this.

247
00:14:01,540 --> 00:14:02,940
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

248
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:04,860
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

249
00:14:05,060 --> 00:14:08,180
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

250
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:12,300
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

251
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:16,980
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

252
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:18,500
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

253
00:14:18,860 --> 00:14:22,260
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

254
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:26,260
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

255
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:30,580
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

256
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:34,140
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

257
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:36,460
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

258
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:40,660
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

259
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:42,740
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

260
00:14:42,740 --> 00:14:44,260
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

261
00:14:44,260 --> 00:14:47,460
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

262
00:14:47,860 --> 00:14:49,780
♪In dreams, it's you♪

263
00:14:49,780 --> 00:14:51,180
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

264
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:54,500
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

265
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:57,900
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

266
00:14:57,900 --> 00:15:01,460
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

267
00:15:01,460 --> 00:15:04,700
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

268
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:08,140
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
